{
  "stem": "19921.7",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "There were a couple of other people there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And of course, the question came up how and who and when and where.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So they said-- they mentioned to me that part of the people went to Belzec and some-- and part of it went to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And that my three brothers and my cousin, which she knew too-- they played together, they went to school together.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "She was younger than I am.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They went with the same transport to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Now, you know Auschwitz-- you go to the left and you go to the right.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Unfortunately, they went to the different direction.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They were sent in a different direction.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Those people were sent to the right direction for them, so they survived.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So I know for a fact that my three brothers and that cousin of mine went to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I also was told that those three brothers, on their way to Belzec-- they were originally sent once to Belzec-- ran away from the train.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were shrewd little kids.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were able to jump out from the train.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was told by that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They returned back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They returned back to Bochnia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And of course, where do they go?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They go again to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And for the second time on the second return, they were taken to Auschwitz when they were liquidating the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And you never heard where your mother was taken?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I never heard with my mother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother, or Belzec or Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I know where my grandparents died.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My grandparents died-- they had a special place for them-- which if I say for them, for all the people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "About seven kilometers away from Bochnia, there was a small town, village town, a farm town, of [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
